WEBVTT

00:00:00.160 --> 00:00:02.750
Good morning family. I have some

00:00:02.760 --> 00:00:06.909
things on my heart today.

00:00:06.919 --> 00:00:10.990
As a prophetic intercessor, I see a

00:00:11.000 --> 00:00:14.150
lot. The Lord and I have a

00:00:14.160 --> 00:00:16.230
real tight relationship about a lot of

00:00:16.240 --> 00:00:19.029
things. I've noticed

00:00:19.039 --> 00:00:20.750
this

00:00:20.760 --> 00:00:22.830
because I try to let you all

00:00:22.840 --> 00:00:26.029
in on things, and I really

00:00:26.039 --> 00:00:28.550
feel it's important that you come up

00:00:28.560 --> 00:00:30.189
higher in your relationship with the

00:00:30.199 --> 00:00:32.190
Lord in

00:00:32.200 --> 00:00:37.110
2024. Let's go higher.

00:00:37.110 --> 00:00:37.120
These

00:00:37.120 --> 00:00:39.190
are

00:00:39.200 --> 00:00:40.950
just conversations I

00:00:40.960 --> 00:00:42.750
have with the Lord, but it's really

00:00:42.760 --> 00:00:44.549
important that I get this across

00:00:44.559 --> 00:00:48.869
to you all because I

00:00:48.869 --> 00:00:48.879
see

00:00:48.879 --> 00:00:50.590
that people are starting

00:00:50.600 --> 00:00:53.349
to notice me on YouTube, in public, or

00:00:55.280 --> 00:00:57.950
when I'm talking to people on the

00:00:57.960 --> 00:01:00.389
phone. When I'm watching

00:01:00.399 --> 00:01:03.389
videos of other

00:01:03.399 --> 00:01:05.789
people,

00:01:05.799 --> 00:01:08.190
people want to do collabs

00:01:08.190 --> 00:01:08.200
or

00:01:08.200 --> 00:01:09.630
have conversations with

00:01:09.640 --> 00:01:11.190
you. It's kind of like

00:01:11.200 --> 00:01:13.950
a dog at a park—I hate to say

00:01:13.950 --> 00:01:13.960
that—but

00:01:13.960 --> 00:01:15.390
when you see a little dog at

00:01:15.400 --> 00:01:17.350
the park, everyone is sniffing everyone.

00:01:17.350 --> 00:01:17.360
They are

00:01:17.360 --> 00:01:18.710
always trying to see who you

00:01:18.720 --> 00:01:19.990
are,

00:01:19.990 --> 00:01:20.000
wanting

00:01:20.000 --> 00:01:21.190
to know your business.

00:01:22.960 --> 00:01:25.630
I deal with dogs; it's just

00:01:25.640 --> 00:01:27.510
the way they are. They are always sniffing

00:01:27.520 --> 00:01:29.149
everything and

00:01:29.159 --> 00:01:30.789
want to know everybody's business. Dogs

00:01:30.799 --> 00:01:33.310
are friendly, but

00:01:33.320 --> 00:01:35.149
sometimes they are

00:01:35.159 --> 00:01:36.710
aggressive, and you have to be cautious

00:01:36.710 --> 00:01:36.720
about

00:01:36.720 --> 00:01:38.389
what kind of dog you

00:01:38.389 --> 00:01:38.399
are

00:01:38.399 --> 00:01:41.109
around. Just being real.

00:01:41.119 --> 00:01:42.389
I don't know if that was a bad

00:01:42.399 --> 00:01:44.350
illustration, but I'm going to go

00:01:44.360 --> 00:01:47.950
with it. When I'm on the phone,

00:01:47.960 --> 00:01:50.030
the Lord prophetically will tell me,

00:01:50.040 --> 00:01:52.149
'He's lying to you'or 'She's lying

00:01:52.159 --> 00:01:55.910
to you.'He'll warn me, 'This

00:01:55.920 --> 00:01:58.870
person has this sin, and

00:01:58.880 --> 00:02:00.550
you need to be cautious of

00:02:00.550 --> 00:02:00.560
this,'especially

00:02:00.560 --> 00:02:01.830
if they want to do business

00:02:01.840 --> 00:02:04.389
with you. A lot of times He'll say, 'No,

00:02:04.399 --> 00:02:07.149
do not do business with that individual.'He'll reveal private things about that individual to me—not

00:02:07.149 --> 00:02:07.159
to gossip, but

00:02:07.159 --> 00:02:12.229
because

00:02:17.720 --> 00:02:20.190
He's warning me. We

00:02:20.190 --> 00:02:20.200
are

00:02:20.200 --> 00:02:21.670
tight; we have a

00:02:21.680 --> 00:02:25.509
relationship. It's like how you

00:02:25.509 --> 00:02:25.519
are

00:02:25.519 --> 00:02:28.390
able to talk to your

00:02:28.390 --> 00:02:28.400
spouse

00:02:28.400 --> 00:02:31.869
and tell them things

00:02:31.879 --> 00:02:33.949
you wouldn't tell anyone else because

00:02:33.949 --> 00:02:33.959
you

00:02:33.959 --> 00:02:35.509
are

00:02:35.509 --> 00:02:35.519
friends.

00:02:35.519 --> 00:02:37.790
I'm going to

00:02:37.800 --> 00:02:40.229
make this a two-part thing, but I

00:02:40.239 --> 00:02:41.470
don't want to touch too much on the

00:02:41.480 --> 00:02:44.790
friendship part of being a friend of

00:02:44.800 --> 00:02:47.270
God yet. What I'm trying to say is

00:02:47.280 --> 00:02:50.070
whenever I'm on the phone with

00:02:50.070 --> 00:02:50.080
an

00:02:50.080 --> 00:02:53.030
individual or if I meet

00:02:53.030 --> 00:02:53.040
them

00:02:53.040 --> 00:02:55.509
in public and they

00:02:55.509 --> 00:02:55.519
want to

00:02:55.519 --> 00:02:57.990
get together

00:02:57.990 --> 00:02:58.000
for

00:02:58.000 --> 00:02:59.869
dinner,

00:02:59.879 --> 00:03:02.070
the Lord says,

00:03:05.120 --> 00:03:06.670
'No.'They

00:03:09.239 --> 00:03:11.789
might get offended,

00:03:11.799 --> 00:03:14.110
but the Lord always tells me

00:03:14.120 --> 00:03:16.550
there's more to this than what

00:03:16.550 --> 00:03:16.560
I

00:03:16.560 --> 00:03:20.509
realize. He's trying to protect me. Do

00:03:20.519 --> 00:03:22.750
you want Him to lead and guide you in

00:03:22.760 --> 00:03:25.550
everything you do or not? God has an

00:03:25.560 --> 00:03:28.670
opinion about everyone. One time, I

00:03:30.360 --> 00:03:34.429
was really hurt by a pastor I

00:03:34.429 --> 00:03:34.439
had

00:03:34.439 --> 00:03:38.550
talked to before.

00:03:38.560 --> 00:03:42.630
The Lord came to me

00:03:42.640 --> 00:03:46.030
and apologized for how that individual

00:03:46.040 --> 00:03:48.990
treated me. He said, 'Brandon, I

00:03:49.000 --> 00:03:51.710
just want to let you know

00:03:51.720 --> 00:03:53.190
that was wrong, and I know your heart

00:03:53.190 --> 00:03:53.200
is hurt.'He

00:03:53.200 --> 00:03:55.190
said, 'I just want to

00:03:55.200 --> 00:03:58.390
apologize on behalf of

00:03:58.390 --> 00:03:58.400
them.'I

00:03:58.400 --> 00:03:59.990
said, 'Lord,

00:04:00.000 --> 00:04:02.509
they had a bad day,

00:04:02.509 --> 00:04:02.519
and

00:04:02.519 --> 00:04:04.910
people have things going on; I

00:04:04.920 --> 00:04:06.949
forgive

00:04:06.949 --> 00:04:06.959
them.'We

00:04:06.959 --> 00:04:08.990
had

00:04:08.990 --> 00:04:09.000
a

00:04:09.000 --> 00:04:11.270
conversation,

00:04:11.270 --> 00:04:11.280
and

00:04:11.280 --> 00:04:13.470
I brought up another

00:04:13.480 --> 00:04:16.670
person. He said, 'Brandon, that

00:04:16.680 --> 00:04:19.189
person's heart is good before Me.

00:04:19.199 --> 00:04:21.189
They wouldn't have done that, and they

00:04:21.199 --> 00:04:23.189
wouldn't have treated you that way.

00:04:23.199 --> 00:04:24.710
I know

00:04:24.720 --> 00:04:26.790
that for a fact. If that person

00:04:28.400 --> 00:04:30.150
would

00:04:30.160 --> 00:04:32.029
have known your telephone number,

00:04:32.039 --> 00:04:34.790
they would have called you personally and never treated you that

00:04:34.790 --> 00:04:34.800
way.'It

00:04:34.800 --> 00:04:39.629
took me back because of the

00:04:39.639 --> 00:04:44.230
way God spoke so highly of this

00:04:44.240 --> 00:04:47.909
individual. It

00:04:47.919 --> 00:04:49.749
made me examine

00:04:49.759 --> 00:04:52.430
myself like

00:04:52.440 --> 00:04:53.230
a

00:04:53.240 --> 00:04:56.430
mirror. If I am able to see prophetically

00:04:56.440 --> 00:04:59.070
when I am standing before a person,

00:05:00.919 --> 00:05:04.189
God will reveal things

00:05:04.199 --> 00:05:05.870
about them—whether they have

00:05:05.880 --> 00:05:08.310
anger issues, lying issues,

00:05:08.320 --> 00:05:10.270
if they are greedy,

00:05:10.270 --> 00:05:10.280
or

00:05:10.280 --> 00:05:12.390
if their motive is not

00:05:12.400 --> 00:05:15.430
pure.

00:05:15.440 --> 00:05:18.350
Caution, caution, caution, or a go,

00:05:18.360 --> 00:05:21.150
go, go! He'll say, 'Yes, this person is good.

00:05:21.160 --> 00:05:24.749
Green means go, buddy!'Or: 'Red

00:05:24.759 --> 00:05:27.309
means stop! Don't do that,

00:05:27.319 --> 00:05:29.390
Brandon; they'll end up ripping

00:05:29.400 --> 00:05:32.590
you off. Stay away

00:05:32.600 --> 00:05:35.469
from them. You can go certain ways

00:05:35.479 --> 00:05:37.150
in certain areas with this

00:05:37.160 --> 00:05:39.950
relationship, but it does not ever go to

00:05:39.960 --> 00:05:42.870
this level. Don't let them in

00:05:42.880 --> 00:05:45.909
your inner circle; they are a gossip and

00:05:45.909 --> 00:05:45.919
will

00:05:45.919 --> 00:05:47.469
backstab

00:05:47.469 --> 00:05:47.479
you.'He

00:05:47.479 --> 00:05:51.510
warns me of

00:05:51.520 --> 00:05:56.029
things. But my question to you is:

00:05:56.039 --> 00:06:00.629
what does God say about you?

00:06:00.639 --> 00:06:04.749
He sees into the depth of your

00:06:04.749 --> 00:06:04.759
heart—all

00:06:04.759 --> 00:06:07.430
the hidden sin, the things

00:06:07.440 --> 00:06:09.270
you think you can fool

00:06:09.270 --> 00:06:09.280
everyone

00:06:09.280 --> 00:06:12.830
else with in the natural world.

00:06:19.039 --> 00:06:20.469
You think you can

00:06:20.479 --> 00:06:21.909
fool your pastor,

00:06:21.909 --> 00:06:21.919
your spouse,

00:06:21.919 --> 00:06:24.510
or who you

00:06:24.510 --> 00:06:24.520
are

00:06:24.520 --> 00:06:28.550
dating, but you can't fool God. He sees

00:06:28.560 --> 00:06:31.270
the depth of who you are

00:06:31.280 --> 00:06:33.629
from the time you were

00:06:33.639 --> 00:06:35.270
created in your mother's womb

00:06:35.280 --> 00:06:36.909
to the day you die.

00:06:39.479 --> 00:06:42.790
Who are you before Him? Yes, we

00:06:42.790 --> 00:06:42.800
are under

00:06:42.800 --> 00:06:46.550
the blood and our sins

00:06:46.560 --> 00:06:49.029
are washed away, but there are character

00:06:49.039 --> 00:06:50.670
issues people don't want

00:06:50.680 --> 00:06:54.710
to take care of. Deep down inside, if

00:06:54.720 --> 00:06:56.990
you were

00:06:57.000 --> 00:06:58.869
to stand before

00:06:58.869 --> 00:06:58.879
a

00:06:58.879 --> 00:07:01.150
prophetic person,

00:07:01.160 --> 00:07:04.309
what would God warn them about

00:07:04.319 --> 00:07:07.869
you? I quickly want to

00:07:07.879 --> 00:07:10.869
examine myself and say, 'God, if I'm

00:07:10.879 --> 00:07:13.550
standing before somebody

00:07:13.550 --> 00:07:13.560
with

00:07:13.560 --> 00:07:15.189
a prophetic

00:07:15.189 --> 00:07:15.199
gift,

00:07:15.199 --> 00:07:18.350
what do they see about

00:07:18.350 --> 00:07:18.360
me?'It's

00:07:18.360 --> 00:07:21.830
not that it matters what they think,

00:07:21.840 --> 00:07:23.749
but it matters what God is relaying to them to

00:07:23.759 --> 00:07:26.230
warn them. He might say, 'They have

00:07:26.240 --> 00:07:27.830
these issues; you don't want to do

00:07:27.840 --> 00:07:30.150
business with

00:07:32.430 --> 00:07:32.440
them.'I'll

00:07:33.960 --> 00:07:36.550
be walking down

00:07:36.560 --> 00:07:38.710
the aisle at Walmart, and the Lord will say, 'Get your

00:07:38.720 --> 00:07:41.390
children close to you now. That man

00:07:41.400 --> 00:07:43.270
is a

00:07:43.280 --> 00:07:47.029
predator;

00:07:47.029 --> 00:07:47.039
he

00:07:47.039 --> 00:07:49.629
has sexual bad things

00:07:49.629 --> 00:07:49.639
toward

00:07:49.639 --> 00:07:51.790
children.'It's

00:07:51.800 --> 00:07:55.990
a warning for protection.

00:07:56.000 --> 00:07:59.149
Don't let them go to that party

00:07:59.159 --> 00:08:01.070
because those

00:08:01.070 --> 00:08:01.080
kids'parents

00:08:01.080 --> 00:08:04.830
are

00:08:04.840 --> 00:08:06.430
loose in the way they raise their

00:08:06.440 --> 00:08:08.550
children. Don't allow them to go

00:08:08.560 --> 00:08:10.670
because they are a mixed

00:08:10.680 --> 00:08:14.909
bag. Does God have an opinion about

00:08:14.919 --> 00:08:19.230
you? Yes, He does. What things do you

00:08:19.240 --> 00:08:21.670
think you're hiding from people

00:08:21.680 --> 00:08:23.950
that you think you're

00:08:23.960 --> 00:08:26.710
fooling everybody else? God sees

00:08:26.720 --> 00:08:29.950
it. I want Him to look at me and say,

00:08:29.960 --> 00:08:31.589
'He's perfect before

00:08:31.599 --> 00:08:34.350
Me. Well done, thou good and faithful

00:08:34.360 --> 00:08:37.469
servant.

00:08:43.919 --> 00:08:46.750
Brandon's a good one.'Do you see

00:08:46.760 --> 00:08:49.630
what I'm trying to say?

00:08:49.640 --> 00:08:53.790
What does God say about

00:08:53.800 --> 00:08:56.670
you? I wanted to come on today

00:08:56.680 --> 00:08:59.590
and tell you to examine your heart.

00:08:59.600 --> 00:09:01.190
It's not about gossip

00:09:01.190 --> 00:09:01.200
or

00:09:01.200 --> 00:09:04.150
trying to

00:09:04.150 --> 00:09:04.160
backbite;

00:09:04.160 --> 00:09:06.949
He always protects those He loves.

00:09:06.959 --> 00:09:09.190
He loves all His children,

00:09:09.200 --> 00:09:11.990
but when

00:09:12.000 --> 00:09:14.590
you have a covenant with

00:09:14.590 --> 00:09:14.600
God—whenever

00:09:14.600 --> 00:09:17.550
you're a tither and

00:09:17.550 --> 00:09:17.560
a

00:09:17.560 --> 00:09:21.110
giver—what's

00:09:21.120 --> 00:09:23.230
mine is His and what's His is

00:09:23.240 --> 00:09:27.269
mine. If He tells me to pray right now, will

00:09:27.269 --> 00:09:27.279
I

00:09:27.279 --> 00:09:29.150
do it? If He tells you to give,

00:09:29.160 --> 00:09:31.829
would you give? If He tells you to

00:09:31.829 --> 00:09:31.839
sow

00:09:31.839 --> 00:09:35.150
$1,000, would you be quick to

00:09:35.160 --> 00:09:37.269
do it because you

00:09:37.269 --> 00:09:37.279
are

00:09:37.279 --> 00:09:40.030
obedient? He

00:09:40.040 --> 00:09:41.550
examines your heart.

00:09:41.560 --> 00:09:44.550
If He says

00:09:44.560 --> 00:09:46.990
go and pray for that person right now because

00:09:46.990 --> 00:09:47.000
they are

00:09:47.000 --> 00:09:48.990
hurting and wanting to hurt

00:09:48.990 --> 00:09:49.000
themselves

00:09:49.000 --> 00:09:50.670
