00:09:52.790 --> 00:09:52.800
Are

00:09:52.800 --> 00:09:56.310
you quick to do these things? Are you a

00:09:56.320 --> 00:09:58.630
gossip, a complainer, or a

00:09:58.640 --> 00:10:01.630
backbiter? Do you talk bad about people

00:10:01.640 --> 00:10:04.750
and ridicule

00:10:04.750 --> 00:10:04.760
them?

00:10:04.760 --> 00:10:07.670
Are you abusive verbally to your

00:10:07.680 --> 00:10:10.310
children or spouse? Do you treat

00:10:10.320 --> 00:10:13.150
them like trash on the way to church and

00:10:13.160 --> 00:10:15.990
then act all holy and sanctimonious?

00:10:18.040 --> 00:10:19.870
Then you get back in

00:10:19.880 --> 00:10:21.750
the car and fuss all the way

00:10:21.760 --> 00:10:24.030
home,

00:10:24.040 --> 00:10:26.069
cussing

00:10:26.079 --> 00:10:27.670
them

00:10:27.680 --> 00:10:30.470
out. Does God look at you?

00:10:33.040 --> 00:10:35.470
When you get real with God, God

00:10:35.470 --> 00:10:35.480
will

00:10:35.480 --> 00:10:38.509
get real with you. He sees even

00:10:38.509 --> 00:10:38.519
when

00:10:38.519 --> 00:10:40.870
