and

00:10:57.480 --> 00:11:00.269
I need some spiritual backing here.

00:11:00.279 --> 00:11:02.509
Where are You at?'He'll say, 'You haven't spent

00:11:02.519 --> 00:11:04.310
enough time in prayer today, Brandon.'It's always me;

00:11:04.310 --> 00:11:04.320
I'm the one

00:11:04.320 --> 00:11:07.710
at

00:11:10.000 --> 00:11:12.310
fault, never God. I'm

00:11:12.320 --> 00:11:13.829
the one with the issue.

00:11:13.839 --> 00:11:16.670
He's perfect, but I

00:11:20.120 --> 00:11:22.949
want to be

00:11:22.959 --> 00:11:25.230
an

00:11:25.240 --> 00:11:28.750
open book. Change me. Create in me

00:11:28.760 --> 00:11:30.949
a clean

00:11:30.959 --> 00:11:32.150
heart,

00:11:32.150 --> 00:11:32.160
O

00:11:32.160 --> 00:11:35.470
God. Search me,

00:11:35.480 --> 00:11:36.509
know

00:11:36.519 --> 00:11:40.509
me, and mold me into who I need to be.

00:11:40.519 --> 00:11:45.389
I hope this

00:11:45.389 --> 00:11:45.399
is

00:11:45.399 --> 00:11:47.230
coming across

00:11:47.230 --> 00:11:47.240
as

00:11:47.240 --> 00:11:49.310
important because I want you

00:11:49.320 --> 00:11:53.389
to know how much Jesus loves you. It

00:11:53.399 --> 00:11:57.430
needs to be more than just a love;

00:11:57.440 --> 00:12:00.910
it needs to be an

00:12:00.920 --> 00:12:04.310
intimacy. What does He say about

00:12:04.320 --> 00:12:06.750
you? What is His heart

00:12:06.750 --> 00:12:06.760
toward

00:12:06.760 --> 00:12:09.430
you?

00:12:09.440 --> 00:12:12.150
I keep saying it over

00:12:12.160 --> 00:12:16.350
and over again because I want to drive it

00:12:16.360 --> 00:12:18.590
home. It's so

00:12:18.600 --> 00:12:20.790
important. When

