He

00:12:20.800 --> 00:12:24.310
lets me examine a person in

00:12:24.320 --> 00:12:26.069
the spirit and warns me about

00:12:26.079 --> 00:12:29.430
them, I know it can be reversed. What

00:12:29.440 --> 00:12:32.629
do they see about me? I know I'm not

00:12:32.639 --> 00:12:35.150
perfect, and my family

00:12:35.150 --> 00:12:35.160
isn't

00:12:35.160 --> 00:12:37.389
perfect,

00:12:37.399 --> 00:12:40.069
but we

00:12:40.069 --> 00:12:40.079
are

00:12:40.079 --> 00:12:42.110
quick to

00:12:42.120 --> 00:12:44.350
repent. We are quick to take

00:12:44.360 --> 00:12:46.790
communion and fall

00:12:46.800 --> 00:12:50.110
at His feet.

00:12:50.120 --> 00:12:53.790
Father, I need You in my

00:12:53.800 --> 00:12:56.189
business dealings, when I'm trying to do

00:12:56.199 --> 00:12:58.829
a car deal or flip

00:12:58.839 --> 00:13:01.150
something on eBay.

00:13:04.240 --> 00:13:07.230
Show me the secret things

00:13:09.399 --> 00:13:13.069
that nobody else can see.

00:13:15.399 --> 00:13:16.790
Part of

00:13:16.800 --> 00:13:18.470
my gifting is that

00:13:18.470 --> 00:13:18.480
He reveals

00:13:18.480 --> 00:13:22.870
hidden things

00:13:22.870 --> 00:13:22.880
to

00:13:22.880 --> 00:13:26.110
me

00:13:26.110 --> 00:13:26.120
about

00:13:26.120 --> 00:13:28.910
investments.

00:13:29.760 --> 00:13:32.870
I'm

00:13:32.880 --> 00:13:36.110
no special person;

00:13:36.120 --> 00:13:38.790
I'm a work in

00:13:38.800 --> 00:13:41.350
progress. But I ask Him

00:13:41.350 --> 00:13:41.360
to

00:13:41.360 --> 00:13:43.590
help me not lose His money

00:13:43.590 --> 00:13:43.600
because

00:13:43.600 --> 00:13:46.350
it's His money;

00:13:46.360 --> 00:13:48.310
I'm just a steward.

00:13:54.759 --> 00:13:57.269
I don't want to bury it in the dirt; I want

00:13:57.279 --> 00:13:58.550
to invest it

00:13:58.560 --> 00:13:59.670
and

00:13:59.680 --> 00:14:01.389
be faithful with a little

00:14:01.389 --> 00:14:01.399
so

00:14:01.399 --> 00:14:04.389
He'll make me ruler over much.

00:14:04.399 --> 00:14:06.269
He'll show me

00:14:06.279 --> 00:14:07.590
investments, and if people try to take

00:14:07.600 --> 00:14:09.430
advantage of me, the

00:14:09.440 --> 00:14:12.150
Lord warns me.

00:14:20.360 --> 00:14:24.509
I always go

00:14:24.519 --> 00:14:27.110
with the love of God, knowing what

00:14:27.110 --> 00:14:27.120
He

00:14:27.120 --> 00:14:30.350
warned me about. They don't

00:14:30.360 --> 00:14:32.550
know that I know what they know.

00:14:32.560 --> 00:14:34.389
He'll

00:14:34.399 --> 00:14:36.629
show me investments

00:14:36.629 --> 00:14:36.639
and

00:14:36.639 --> 00:14:37.829
highlight them.

00:14:37.839 --> 00:14:38.949
Sometimes I'll say, 'This one

00:14:38.959 --> 00:14:40.470
is going to be

00:14:40.470 --> 00:14:40.480
good,'and

00:14:40.480 --> 00:14:42.310
it's just

00:14:42.320 --> 00:14:44.550
conversation. Someone

00:14:44.550 --> 00:14:44.560
once asked

00:14:44.560 --> 00:14:46.150
if I

00:14:46.150 --> 00:14:46.160
invested in

00:14:46.160 --> 00:14:49.389
those things. No, because I'm not

00:14:49.399 --> 00:14:51.829
after greed; it's about

00:14:51.829 --> 00:14:51.839
the

00:14:51.839 --> 00:14:54.389
relationship. I want to

00:14:54.399 --> 00:14:57.189
know every secret thing He has. I want to

00:14:57.199 --> 00:14:59.550
lay my head upon His chest and

00:14:59.560 --> 00:15:02.470
know His breath when He exhales

00:15:02.480 --> 00:15:04.910
and inhales. I want

00:15:04.920 --> 00:15:07.030
to know everything about

00:15:07.040 --> 00:15:11.430
Him. The Holy

00:15:11.440 --> 00:15:14.670
Spirit has a

00:15:14.680 --> 00:15:17.829
fragrance—every

00:15:17.839 --> 00:15:20.389
single thing about Him.

00:15:20.399 --> 00:15:22.230
When

00:15:22.240 --> 00:15:26.030
He's having a hard day with His

00:15:26.040 --> 00:15:30.350
kids, I can feel it. I

00:15:30.350 --> 00:15:30.360
asked,

00:15:30.360 --> 00:15:33.870
'Father, are You okay today?'He said,

00:15:33.880 --> 00:15:36.269
'Brandon, my children were

00:15:36.279 --> 00:15:38.990
very disobedient today.'I

00:15:38.990 --> 00:15:39.000
could feel

00:15:39.000 --> 00:15:40.949
He was agitated.

00:15:40.959 --> 00:15:43.189
When you get to

00:15:43.199 --> 00:15:44.790
know somebody, you know when they

00:15:44.790 --> 00:15:44.800
are

00:15:44.800 --> 00:15:47.269
agitated. I don't want to be super

00:15:47.279 --> 00:15:51.030
religious, but

00:16:00.160 --> 00:16:02.550
He shows me

00:16:02.560 --> 00:16:05.389
colors. Colors are big in the spirit

00:16:05.399 --> 00:16:08.110
realm.

00:16:11.680 --> 00:16:13.629
When you get close to God, He shows

00:16:13.639 --> 00:16:16.430
you big secret things.

00:16:16.440 --> 00:16:20.150
I see colors around things

00:16:20.160 --> 00:16:22.110
as

00:16:22.120 --> 00:16:25.309
warnings—blacks,

00:16:25.319 --> 00:16:28.949
purples, pinks.

00:16:28.959 --> 00:16:31.030
I know it's stuff they

00:16:31.030 --> 00:16:31.040
are

00:16:31.040 --> 00:16:32.790
dealing with; they are prayer

00:16:32.800 --> 00:16:35.470
cues. It's about

00:16:35.480 --> 00:16:38.389
atmospheres. I can go into a church, and

00:16:38.399 --> 00:16:41.790
the Lord will warn me about what's

00:16:41.800 --> 00:16:44.350
going on with the pastor. He'll say, 'Don't go to

00:16:44.360 --> 00:16:46.749
church here. You need to get out

00:16:46.759 --> 00:16:50.269
quick. Don't trust them

00:16:50.279 --> 00:16:53.269
about spiritual

00:16:53.269 --> 00:16:53.279
giftings.'The

00:16:53.279 --> 00:16:55.069
pastor might be jealous

00:16:55.069 --> 00:16:55.079
and

00:16:55.079 --> 00:16:57.509
want competition.

00:16:57.519 --> 00:16:59.629
He'll warn me about

00:16:59.639 --> 00:17:02.269
atmospheres. I'm very sensitive

00:17:02.279 --> 00:17:03.309
to

00:17:03.309 --> 00:17:03.319
them.

00:17:03.319 --> 00:17:05.710
People ask

00:17:05.710 --> 00:17:05.720
to

00:17:05.720 --> 00:17:06.990
go out to dinner,

00:17:06.990 --> 00:17:07.000
but

00:17:07.000 --> 00:17:10.069
I don't go

00:17:10.079 --> 00:17:12.990
because

00:17:13.000 --> 00:17:15.350
I protect the

00:17:15.360 --> 00:17:18.189
gift inside of me. I

00:17:18.189 --> 00:17:18.199
don't

00:17:18.199 --> 00:17:20.470
go out flippantly.

00:17:22.679 --> 00:17:25.189
At Christmas, my

00:17:25.199 --> 00:17:26.710
family wanted me to go over, but

00:17:26.710 --> 00:17:26.720
I

00:17:26.720 --> 00:17:28.909
stayed

00:17:28.909 --> 00:17:28.919
with

00:17:28.919 --> 00:17:31.029
my wife and

00:17:31.029 --> 00:17:31.039
kids.

00:17:31.039 --> 00:17:34.070
It's

00:17:34.080 --> 00:17:35.830
not that I'm better; I'm just

00:17:35.840 --> 00:17:39.830
very sensitive to

00:17:42.160 --> 00:17:44.549
atmospheres and watchful over

00:17:44.559 --> 00:17:47.190
where I put myself.

00:17:47.190 --> 00:17:47.200
I

00:17:47.200 --> 00:17:48.470
don't

00:17:48.480 --> 00:17:49.789
just go

00:17:49.799 --> 00:17:52.029
