00:17:54.679 --> 00:17:57.950
unless I have an inkling

00:17:57.960 --> 00:18:00.750
the Holy Spirit says

00:18:00.750 --> 00:18:00.760
to

00:18:00.760 --> 00:18:04.590
do it. I'm an

00:18:04.600 --> 00:18:08.230
intercessor; I seek His

00:18:08.240 --> 00:18:12.029
face. My safe

00:18:12.039 --> 00:18:14.390
