00:18:25.960 --> 00:18:27.669
I don't want

00:18:27.679 --> 00:18:30.390
to be rude, but 99% of

00:18:30.390 --> 00:18:30.400
the time,

00:18:30.400 --> 00:18:32.590
I'm going to say no.

00:18:40.080 --> 00:18:44.190
I just wanted to let you

00:18:44.190 --> 00:18:44.200
know me

00:18:44.200 --> 00:18:47.870
more. I hope

00:18:47.870 --> 00:18:47.880
that blessed

00:18:47.880 --> 00:18:49.470
you. It's important to the Father. If

00:18:49.480 --> 00:18:50.669
you want to come up higher,

00:18:52.640 --> 00:18:55.950
you'll work on this stuff.

00:19:00.000 --> 00:19:02.390
Let me pray for you. Father, I

00:19:02.400 --> 00:19:03.390
thank You

00:19:03.400 --> 00:19:06.070
for every single person

00:19:06.080 --> 00:19:09.070
represented here. May

00:19:09.070 --> 00:19:09.080
they

00:19:09.080 --> 00:19:10.870
come up higher in their

00:19:10.880 --> 00:19:14.430
relationship with You. It's all about

00:19:14.440 --> 00:19:18.270
falling in love with Jesus

00:19:18.270 --> 00:19:18.280
and

00:19:18.280 --> 00:19:21.750
having intimacy with the Holy

00:19:21.760 --> 00:19:24.590
Spirit.

00:19:39.200 --> 00:19:41.789
Ultimately, it's about falling in love

00:19:41.799 --> 00:19:44.390
more with Jesus on a day-to-day

00:19:44.400 --> 00:19:47.230
basis.

00:19:47.240 --> 00:19:50.750
I thank You that

00:19:50.760 --> 00:19:52.990
every person

00:19:53.000 --> 00:19:55.149
