00:21:01.039 --> 00:21:03.990
I thank You that

00:21:03.990 --> 00:21:04.000
they are

00:21:04.000 --> 00:21:05.789
healed and whole

00:21:05.799 --> 00:21:08.350
because

00:21:08.360 --> 00:21:11.230
Christ redeemed us from the curse of the

00:21:11.240 --> 00:21:14.710
